## Persistence Hierarchy

From most ephemeral to most durable:

| Layer | Location | Loaded When |
|-------|----------|-------------|
| Conversation | (in-context) | Always — volatile |
| Temp files | `tmp/` | Per-task, gitignored |
{%#if sessionHandoff%}| Memory | `{%systemDir%}/memory/` | On demand |
{%/if%}| Skills | `{%systemDir%}/skills/*/SKILL.md` | When triggered |
| Rules | `{%systemDir%}/rules/*.md` | Every session |
| **{%governanceFile%}** | `./{%governanceFile%}` | **Every session** |

