## Security Rules

- Never read `.env` files or echo credentials
- Never install third-party MCP servers/plugins without explicit approval
- Never write outside this workspace root — use project-local `tmp/`, not system `/tmp/`
- Approved tools only — ask before using new tools/APIs

---

## Quality Rules
{%#if isProductionQuality%}
- QC is a structural gate, not an optional post-step
- Run spot-checks after every 5 items in batch work (Ralph Loop)
- Combined agents (extract + classify) beat split agents on quality
- Disagreements between agents reveal ambiguity — escalate, don't suppress
{%/if%}
{%#if hasQualityGates%}
{%#unless isProductionQuality%}- QC is a structural gate, not an optional post-step
- Run QC checkpoints at regular intervals during batch work
- All results must be reviewed before being marked complete
{%/unless%}
{%/if%}
{%#unless hasQualityGates%}- Run a quick check before finishing any task
- Review outputs before marking work complete
{%/unless%}

